  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育系统的风险响应流程建一个流程图。核心场景是：当Education_ContentCDN触发异常时，系统需要根据风险等级走不同的修复路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点是ContentCDN。那风险等级判断放在哪个节点？我注意到GradeSync模块通常负责成绩数据同步，它适合作为决策点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Education_GradeSync作为决策节点很合适。它可以根据异常影响范围判断风险等级：高、中高、中低三档。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主干：从ContentCDN到GradeSync的菱形判断节点，然后分三条分支。高风险直接回到ContentCDN做紧急隔离，中高也是回ContentCDN做标准修复，中低风险则导向LMS门户做降级处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，三条分支最后要汇聚。高风险和中高虽然都回ContentCDN，但修复策略不同，需要区分；中低走LMS门户降级后，也要统一到最终的数据持久化环节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我加一个汇聚节点F，让三条分支都指向F，再从F连到StudentDB。这样结构清晰：C、D、E都到F，F再到G。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，F作为统一处理节点，G是Education_StudentDB负责最终数据落库。不过C和D都是指向ContentCDN，标签要区分清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，B到C标\"高\"，B到D标\"中高\"，B到E标\"中/低\"。C和D虽然都是ContentCDN，但代表不同的修复实例。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，C和D的指向有问题。我刚才说的是高风险和中高都回ContentCDN做修复，但流程图里C和D之后还要到F。让我重新理一下：C是紧急修复后的ContentCDN状态，D是标准修复后的状态，它们都要进入F这个验证节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，C和D是修复完成后的中间状态，不是循环回起点。E是LMS门户降级后的状态，三者都汇聚到F做最终验证，再到StudentDB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "F节点我定义为统一验证与审计节点，所有风险处置完成后都要经过它，确保数据一致性，最后写入StudentDB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "流程已更新：A→B判断，三分支C/D/E，汇聚到F，F→G。节点标签保持业务语义，不暴露内部编号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再确认一下E到F的流向：LMS门户降级处理后，数据状态也要经过F验证，这个没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，E→F已连接。三条分支C→F、D→F、E→F全部汇聚，再从F→G到StudentDB。流程闭合。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后检查一下：A是ContentCDN起点，B是GradeSync决策，C/D是不同等级的CDN修复，E是LMS降级，F是统一验证，G是StudentDB落库。逻辑完整。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "流程图最终确认：七个节点，A起始，B菱形判断三分支，C/D/E并行处理，F汇聚，G终止。所有流向和标签符合风险响应业务规则。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，这个流程图可以交付了。覆盖了从CDN异常触发、GradeSync分级决策、多路径修复到最终数据入库的完整闭环。",
